query:
DELETE FROM casbin_rule WHERE
                    ptype = $1 AND
                    (v2 is NULL OR v2 = COALESCE($2,v2)) AND
                    (v3 is NULL OR v3 = COALESCE($3,v3)) AND
                    (v4 is NULL OR v4 = COALESCE($4,v4)) AND
                    (v5 is NULL OR v5 = COALESCE($5,v5))
